  <brief_title>Effect of an Antioxidant on Cancer-Cachectic Patients Undergoing Exercise Training</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of N-Acetylcysteine on Skeletal Muscle in Cachectic Cancer Patients Undergoing a Resistance Training Program (Phase 2 Study)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
